<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="ida89650fd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2001—Par. (4). <ref href="/us/pl/107/107">Pub. L. 107–107</ref> added par. (4).</p>
</note>
