<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="ida89650ff-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 2001 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Amendment by <ref href="/us/pl/107/107">Pub. L. 107–107</ref> effective as if included in the enactment of this chapter by <ref href="/us/pl/106/398">Pub. L. 106–398</ref>, see <ref href="/us/pl/107/107/s711/f">section 711(f) of Pub. L. 107–107</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s1111">section 1111 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
